title: Matchbox Twenty *LIVE* - SoundStage Presentation
description:
Rob Thomas and the gang put on a quaint little concert for their female fans in this fluffy Sound Stage presentation capped from Music-HD. This small venue allows them the freedom to do some "unplugged" and re-arranged versions of some of their popular hits. There's also some interaction from the band explaining some of the songs, arrangements, and stories and gives a look inside the band itself.  

We're not too particularly fond of the band ourselves but, a nice lady friend of ours made this request so, we upped it for her and all those romantics in PB land! 
 
This 41 minute (approx) mini-concert includes such hits as "3 A.M.", "A Different Side of Me", "Slow Dancin'", "Crutch", "Real World", and more.
